<h2 id='update-a-sub-account-39-s-options'>Update a sub account&#39;s options</h2>
<p>Update a sub account&#39;s options under the master account</p>

<blockquote>
<p>Definition</p>
</blockquote>
<div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight shell tab-shell"><code>PATCH https://api.zoom.us/v2/accounts/<span class="o">{</span>accountId<span class="o">}</span>/options
</code></pre></div>
<blockquote>
<p>Example Request</p>
</blockquote>
<div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight shell tab-shell"><code><span class="nv">$ </span>curl https://api.zoom.us/v2/accounts/<span class="o">{</span>accountId<span class="o">}</span>/options <span class="se">\</span>
   <span class="nt">-d</span> <span class="s1">'{
    "share_rc": "boolean",
    "room_connectors": "string",
    "share_mc": "boolean",
    "meeting_connectors": "string",
    "pay_mode": "string"
}'</span>
</code></pre></div>
<blockquote>
<p>Example Response</p>
</blockquote>
<div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight plaintext"><code>204 No Content
</code></pre></div>
<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Path Arguments</th>
<th>&nbsp;</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>accountId <strong>required</strong></td>
<td>The account ID</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>

<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Body Arguments</th>
<th>&nbsp;</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>share_rc <em>optional</em><div class="default">false</div></td>
<td>Enable Share Virtual Room Connector</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>room_connectors <em>optional</em></td>
<td>Virtual Room Connector, multiple value separated by comma</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>share_mc <em>optional</em><div class="default">false</div></td>
<td>Enable Share Meeting Connector</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>meeting_connectors <em>optional</em></td>
<td>Meeting Connector, multiple values separated by comma</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>pay_mode <em>optional</em><div class="default">master</div></td>
<td>Payee<div class="enum"><code>master</code> Master account holder pays<br/><code>sub</code> Sub account holder pays<br/></div></td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
